From d5971a40819435b62b5a12be5b2a8b4f366ef74f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Th=C3=A9o-Paul=20Bodin?= <theo-paul.bodin@softathome.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Apr 2025 17:56:41 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] miniupnpd: Load all backends connect all buses
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Problem: Netmodel need pcb backend to work

Solution: Load all backends instead of just ubus

Issue: [UPnP][REG]The DUT Advertise WANIPConnection instead of WANPPPConnection [change]

References: PCF-1833, FEAT-13

Signed-off-by: Théo-Paul Bodin <theo-paul.bodin@softathome.com>
Signed-off-by: Xavier DOOMS <xavier.dooms_ext@softathome.com>
---
 miniupnpd/amx/amxmisc.c    | 103 ++++++++++++++++++++++---------------
 miniupnpd/amx/amxmisc.h    |   2 +-
 miniupnpd/amx/amxpinhole.c |   2 +-
 miniupnpd/amx/amxrdr.c     |  10 ++--
 miniupnpd/miniupnpd.c      |  12 ++---
 miniupnpd/options.c        |   4 +-
 miniupnpd/options.h        |   4 +-
 miniupnpd/upnpglobalvars.c |   4 +-
 miniupnpd/upnpglobalvars.h |   8 +--
 9 files changed, 85 insertions(+), 64 deletions(-)

